fields.Title: PIER / APARTMENTS PIER DOOR
fields.OverrideDialogueCondition: Variable["pier.apartments_door_opens"] == true  or  CheckItem("key_apartment_building")  and  Variable["XP.got_into_the_apartment_building"] == true

fields.Title: Visual Calculus: "Backyard door? There must be anothe..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Backyard door? There must be another entrance to the east.

fields.Title: You: "Am I?"
fields.Dialogue Text: Am I?

fields.Title: Southwest Entrance to the Tenements: "There is no reply. Just faint sweep..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There is no reply. Just faint sweeping sounds inside.

fields.Title: Authority: "You already tried and all you got w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You already tried and all you got was *hurt*. Better not to try anymore. Then you won't get HURT.

fields.Title: Authority: "You're well versed in the kind of t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You're well versed in the kind of threatening legalese that implies criminal liability but in fact has no meaning whatsoever.

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "Ah! It's like a carrot to the stick..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Ah! It's like a carrot to the stick, sort of.

fields.Title: Southwest Entrance to the Tenements: "No reply. You can hear faint sweepi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: No reply. You can hear faint sweeping inside; a gust of wind blows through your clothes.

fields.Title: Southwest Entrance to the Tenements: "The door rattles against your knuck..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The door rattles against your knuckles, but there's no response.

fields.Title: You: ""Hold on, who am I speaking to?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Hold on, who am I speaking to?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""No, you're not.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "No, you're not."

fields.Title: Cleaning Lady: ""It doesn't matter who I am. Now go..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It doesn't matter who I am. Now go on, get out of here!"

fields.Title: Cleaning Lady: ""Hold your horses..." You hear the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Hold your horses..." You hear the click of a night latch, before the lady on the other side gets caught in a coughing spasm.

fields.Title: You: ""Ma'am, your non-compliance is hind..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Ma'am, your non-compliance is hindering a police matter. I may be forced to refer you for potential prosecution."

fields.Title: You: ""Okay, miss, would it help if I sho..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay, miss, would it help if I showed you my badge?"

fields.Title: Southwest Entrance to the Tenements: "A sturdy metal door guards the sout..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A sturdy metal door guards the southwest entrance to the apartment building. It's locked.

fields.Title: You: ""But I'm not joking.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "But I'm not joking."

fields.Title: Authority: "Insufficiently deferential!"
fields.Dialogue Text: Insufficiently deferential!

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Miss," the lieutenant jumps in, "w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Miss," the lieutenant jumps in, "would it help if we offered to show you our badges?"

fields.Title: Cleaning Lady: ""I don't care about your stinkin' b..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't care about your stinkin' badge. Just come in," she manages to say with a wheeze.

fields.Title: You: ""Hey, are you there? I've checked t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Hey, are you there? I've checked the backyard, but couldn't get in that way."

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["backyard.smoker_greeting_done"] == true  and  Variable["pier.apartments_door_whitecheck_reveal"] == true  and  CheckItem("key_apartment_building") == false

fields.Title: You: ""I need to talk to a young man in t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I need to talk to a young man in this building."

fields.Title: You: "Knock again."
fields.Dialogue Text: Knock again.

fields.Title: Cleaning Lady: ""No, I already told you, I won't be..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No, I already told you, I won't be responsible for any more strangers getting into the building..."

fields.Title: You: ""Open up or I'm gonna breach this m..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Open up or I'm gonna breach this motherfucker!" (Kick the door.)

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Madam, I assure you we're real pol..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Madam, I assure you we're real police officers," the lieutenant repeats dutifully.

fields.Title: You: "Convince her that you're a real pol..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Convince her that you're a real policeman.

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["backyard.smoker_greeting_done"] == true  and  Variable["pier.apartments_door_whitecheck_reveal"] == true  and  Variable["pier.apartments_door_real_whitecheck_reveal"] == true  and  IsTaskActive("TASK.find_a_way_inside_apt_building")

fields.Title: Authority: "You can't think of anything convinc..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You can't think of anything convincing. Time for some police brutality!

fields.Title: Cleaning Lady: ""Stop banging on the door! I'm not..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Stop banging on the door! I'm not letting any more strangers inside."

fields.Title: You: ""Kim, tell her we're real policemen!""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Kim, tell her we're real policemen!"

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "From within comes the faint sound o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: From within comes the faint sound of a broom sweeping across the concrete floor.

fields.Title: Visual Calculus: "This could be a way into the apartm..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This could be a way into the apartment building the smoking man vanished into.

fields.Title: Cleaning Lady: ""Go check the backyard door, maybe..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Go check the backyard door, maybe someone there will..." She trails off, leaving the sentence unfinished.

fields.Title: You: ""Ma'am, if you don't open this door..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Ma'am, if you don't open this door, I'm gonna introduce you to a lateral vascular neck restraint -- and it's going to *hurt*."

fields.Title: Cleaning Lady: ""I know my rights! And don't you 'm..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I know my rights! And don't you 'ma'am' me, boy!" the voice snaps back.

fields.Title: Cleaning Lady: ""You don't scare me, punk! I may be..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You don't scare me, punk! I may be an old woman but I can still take the likes of you!"

fields.Title: You: ""Please, let me inside. It's cold o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Please, let me inside. It's cold out here."

fields.Title: Cleaning Lady: ""The police?! Everyone knows the po..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The police?! Everyone knows the police don't come around *here*. The hallways echoes with her cackle.

fields.Title: You: "(Lie.) "I've got my badge right her..."
fields.Dialogue Text: (Lie.) "I've got my badge right here, if you want to see it."

fields.Title: You: ""Ma'am, we're looking for Billie M..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Ma'am, we're looking for Billie Mjean's apartment. We have important news to deliver."

fields.Title: Authority: "Obviously. Look at that vague yet t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Obviously. Look at that vague yet threatening stuff spewing forth from your mouth...

fields.Title: You: "Knock."
fields.Dialogue Text: Knock.

fields.Title: You: "[Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Leave.]

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "But the sweeping on the other side..."
fields.Dialogue Text: But the sweeping on the other side has stopped.

fields.Title: Southwest Entrance to the Tenements: "The door rattles again, but this ti..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The door rattles again, but this time you hear an elderly woman's voice calling out from inside...

fields.Title: Interfacing: "Backyard door? With the smoker? You..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Backyard door? With the smoker? You already were there. Didn't work.

fields.Title: You: ""I'm gonna light this place up!" (R..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm gonna light this place up!" (Roll up your sleeves.)

fields.Title: You: ""This is the police -- open the doo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "This is the police -- open the door."

fields.Title: Cleaning Lady: ""Good. We've had enough problems wi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Good. We've had enough problems with bums and drunks and thieves loitering in the hallway... You have no business here."
